metadata.name: Firehydrant
metadata.description:
These pieces represent my artistic vision for photography: capturing spectacular places around the world; carefully composing each shot; and thoughtfully editing with striking, moody tones that evoke wonder in the viewer.
Each of these artfully curated images is presented as a unique 1/1 edition. NFT buyers will be granted access to the original high resolution image file along with a personal use license and full resolution poster in wooden plate (60*90cm).
